{"tid":1716713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個方法令朝早行動更易成功","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:21:05.000Z","uid":76600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b569930a8b6180f58b9eff6289a5c6de85a9a86","tid":1716713,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"今日路面情況令我有個諗法，可能可以幫到我地朝早抗爭更易成功。<br />\n首先講返今日個情況先，今朝一早路面基本上癱瘓左九成，手足只係主力塞鐵就可以完成罷工。<br />\n<br />\n相比起昨日同前日，手足要同時塞鐵加塞路，今日行動上明顯比較輕鬆。原因係我地係同一時間只需要專注一個行動，唔洗分散行動。成功率自然會大大提高。<br />\n<br />\n咁問題黎喇，即係我地只要係前一晚開花set RB，令佢地唔可以係天光之前清路。咁我地朝早塞埋鐵就可以全港罷工。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，即係我地早一晚塞定路，做定朝早個份先。但係RB要數量多同難清理。拖到第二日。<br />\n<br />\n係突發諗到，所以只可以用紙筆好柒咁畫個time line出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望可以幫到手足，聽日我會繼續出黎塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人報仇，唔好再示弱，你有冇面見中大手足呀？<br />\n有冇面第日係煲底相見？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9QFH89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9QFH89.png&h=dd262e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6380933ef23ef7dba82044e16f8e33ba0ba6b9c5","tid":1716713,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"1114 繼續三罷"},{"pid":"70d345f03056196452665bc08fe74f04fa51b0d5","tid":1716713,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dquBwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dquBwE.jpg&h=978a8d30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"653fcadf28d6cf4ef34f60c035b8f8adee5649ac","tid":1716713,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMeWgwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMeWgwQ.jpg&h=4dc606d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"541e955609c64be02e465c1c87f2ba5e04321550","tid":1716713,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":